&lt;p&gt;We are looking for transport drivers with a full clean licence to join the team during these busy times. We have various shifts upto full time available for people that are able to commit to lines of work upto 12 weeks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates who have PCV/Bus licences would be welcomed also.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hourly rate starts at £10.12 per hour, and may vary depending on what hours are worked I.e evenings or weekends.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;bankrecruitment@uhbw.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
